title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Madhya Pradesh Urban Services for the Poor

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Madhya Pradesh Urban Services for the Poor) is a component of Madhya Pradesh Urban Services for the Poor reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £6,040,870. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Basic drinking water supply and basic sanitation, Democratic participation and civil society, Urban development and management. , with the following implementing partners: ICF Consulting Services Ltd. The start date is 01-06-2006 and the end date is 31-12-2012.
